Package: helper-fun
Title: Workflow Helpers, Color Palettes, and Themes
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Rowland", email = "christopher.r.rowland@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "Director, Clinical Data Science")
Description: Provides corporate color palettes, ggplot2 themes,
    and workflow helper functions for consistent branding across clinical trial 
    visualizations. Includes functions for generating color ramps, discrete and 
    continuous color scales, fill scales using the official TG color scheme,
    custom ggplot2 themes, PowerPoint export utilities for editable graphics,
    flextable formatting helpers for summary tables, data import/export 
    utilities for Excel, CSV, SAS, XPT, and Microsoft Access files, and
    date manipulation helpers for partial date imputation and time conversions.
